        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> and peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Heat a separate pot with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1681816642342-x200.jpg",
