            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to cover the bottom of the pan!) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>breaded chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the outside is golden</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
      "order": 6,
