    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>curry sauce</strong> to a medium heat to reheat</p><p>Top the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with the <strong>chicken katsu</strong> then spoon over the <strong>curry sauce</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>quick-pickled ginger salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
